<div class="height: 0; overflow: hidden; clear: both">
</div>
    <p>The Azure StorSimple solution can make use of the hybrid storage arrays of the StorSimple 5000 and 7000 Series, provide primary SAN storage in the internal environment through SSD and HDD, and connect tightly to Azure, enabling the primary storage to obtain high scalability and distributing capacity in line with requirements. And the hybrid storage arrays of StorSimple 5000 and 7000 Series also provide protection function for the off-site data through the cloud backup and efficient disaster recovery. This StorSimple solution (using appliances of the 5000 and 7000 series) enables customers to deal with the rapid growth of data with devices with small capacity, simplify management of the storage system, and benefit from the economics of the cloud.</p>
    <p>For more details, please refer to the <a id="storsimple_link" style="color: #00a8d9;" href="/zh-cn/solutions/storsimple/">StorSimple</a> web page</p>
